casebody.data:
Anthony DOVE
v.
Nicholaus HARVEY, (correct: "Nicholas E. Harvey, Sr.") No. 174P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. January 26, 2006. Anthony Dove, Pro Se. Thomas H. Morris, Kinston, Kimberly A. Connor, for Nicholaus Harvey.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 31st day of March 2005 by Plaintiff in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 26th day of January 2006."

Justice MARTIN recused.
